            <p align="justify"> <span class="content-full-width style11">Ayurveda, literally means the science of life (Ayur = Life, Veda = Science) and dates back to five thousand years. The ancient Vedic literature by sages has clearly laid out instructions to maintain good health and fight illness through therapies, massages, herbal medicines, diet control and exercise.Ayurvedic therapies offer tried and tested solutions that can help individuals to maintain good health, vitality and energy , thus improving their quality of life. </span>  </br>  </br>
